Author: JollyGood
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Clearly it is a scam.  It was all hype intended to make money like 99% of other ICOs  All official website links, Twitter URL, Telegram... all are dead. Just Reddit has a post saying they have partnered with Coinexis.  They claim to have "partnered with Coinexis" but going to the Coinexis website immediately bring you to a WP template ICO page where Coinexis itself is raising money for an ICO. They have 112 members on their Coinexis Telegram chat at the moment.  It is very convenient timing they "partnered with Coinexis".  The whole thing is a scam.

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Stox to boost Vibeo’s Token Sale with launch of sponsored predictions  Stox has partnered with blockchain-based instant messaging app Vibeo in support of their upcoming Token Sale. Stox will allow platform users to make predictions on the Vibeo Token Sale, comprising of a 700,000 VBEO prize pool.   Vibeo is a social media instant messaging app that includes added features of conference video calls, offline messages, a timeline blog and an interactive map that shows nearby friends and shops. With an authentic integrated crypto wallet, Vibeo users can send and receive funds to friends and make payments to nearby merchants. During its Token Sale, beginning on 17th September 2018, 450m VBEO tokens (priced at 1 VBEO = 0.0001ETH) will be up for grabs, with a hard cap of 40,000ETH.   Stox is a decentralised Ethereum-based prediction markets platform, where people can bet on anything from sports and politics to tech events and ICOs. Niv Abramovich, Stox CMO, welcomed Vibeo to its extensive list of ICO predictions:   We’re proud to offer predictions on the Vibeo Token Sale and excited to see how the app will develop following its Token Sale. Its proprietary technologies, industry know-how and experienced team has all the ingredients to change the social media landscape.   Eric Dechaux, Vibeo founder and CEO, commented:   It’s great to have Stox partner with us during a pivotal stage as we head towards our Token Sale. Stox’s attractive prize pool means that it is the perfect partner to help promote our sale globally. We’re hoping to gain maximum traction during the sale that will enable us to further develop technologies for our instant-messaging app capabilities.   The Vibeo platform is readily-available to download on the Apple App Store and Google Play Store. Vibeo has a rating of 4.4 out of 5 on ICO Bench. For more information about its Token Sale, visit https://vibeo.io/

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Hi Mbally!  Vibeo will be the first REAL decentralized Social and Messaging app in the market. Our v4 will use a decentralized blockchain DB to store users information and a decentralized blockchain mapping system for the Vibeo map (Gotaki system).  Vibeo makes it easier for people to stay connected by providing services to friends, family, businesses, and customers. More than just a messenger service, Vibeo is an all-inclusive messaging ecosphere that integrates online shopping, social media, and messaging into one, easy-to-use app.  And yes we will compete with the major giants such as WeChat and WhatsApp, we are offering something different and new so we should be able to grab a big chunk of their market, we target 250MM user in the coming 5 years for the Vibeo community!

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: The idea is that merchants or people that want to show up on the blockchain map will have to buy the Vibeo API and/or buy VBEO token to register. The more vbeo users we have the more interesting it is for merchants to be on the vibeo map and the more expensive it gets if we grow the user base. The idea is that the VBEO token will be more valuable as Vibeo is getting popular as being the best blockchain instant messaging app.

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: A NEW ERA OF INSTANT MESSAGING/SOCIAL APP ALLOWING ACCESS TO A BLOCKCHAIN COMMUNITY AND ECONOMY  Be Part Of The Innovation - Get Your 10,000 VBEO Tokens For 1 ETH                              Vibeo is building a new era of Instant Messaging/Social app which allow to access a Worldwide blockchain economy and community. Our application is already available for download on App Store and Google Play.  With our integrated crypto wallet, users will be able to send and receive crypto-currencies, carry out exchanges within the community of Vibeo users and use crypto-currencies to make payments from within the application. Users can exchange crypto for goods and services with registered merchants around the world, and can even interact with such merchants (such as making orders or bookings) from the chat app.  In communicating with loved ones, the Vibeo app gives much more functionalities than conventional applications with Advanced Location features that offer travel updates to selected loved ones or groups, currency transfer from one user to another, the creation of a strong community revolving around a decentralized economy.  Merchants who sign up to be listed on the platform would have the benefit of being able to carry out transactions within chats, receive payments, and be listed on the map that would be within the application. In registering as a merchant, an annual fee of $29. The merchants could also get extra visibility features on the map and other advertising features in certain parts of the application at extra costs of between $5.99 to $10.99.   Screenshots from v3.1    Our Roadmap  Starting September 18th. PRE-SALE  TOKEN SALE OVERVIEW  In launching the Vibeo Network, the company would be implementing a Token Sale offering in creating VBEO tokens which would be organized around a smart contract running on the Ethereum Network. The Token Sale is expected to last nine weeks with the pre-sale starting on September 18, 2018.  Sept.18th/Oct.2sd     Pre-Sale (whitelisted)     Bonus 35% Oct.2sd/Oct.12th       Public Sale                    Bonus 20% Oct.12th/Oct.21th      Public Sale                    Bonus 10% Oct.21th/Nov.30th      Public Sale                    Bonus 5%  TOKEN NAME:  VBEO Token  TOKEN SUPPLY:  The total token supply is nine hundred and fifty million (950,000,000) four hundred and twenty-five million tokens (425,000,000) will be made available for public distribution with a maximum cap of 40,000 ETH.   RATE:  The expected price per token is 10,000 VBEO per 1 ETH or 1 VBEO=0.0001 ETH.

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Hi Max, I am Eric the founder of Vibeo.  You are totally wrong and I actually feel your post is offending to all my team who are working very hard on this project. We are indeed 15 people and the team will grow to 22 in the coming weeks. Let me answer your points:  -I invite you to contact each member of the team through LinkedIn to verify if they are working on Vibeo. -Most of the team are from Bulgaria, except me, I am from Canada with grand parents from Bulgaria so I know this country very well. I ll be soon leaving Canada to take care of my team full time, our CCO Mira is also from bulgaria but she is actually living in USA. All my advisors are from different country except Kalin which is also from Bulgaria. I invite you to check my twitter feed, and you will see I am travelling a lot, even to personally meet with my advisors (actually very few people does that in the ICO field!). -I don't have any dev from Russia, you are talking about Mikhail, he is not a dev but our sys admin, taking care of the entire infrastructure, I know him for many years and this is someone I trust, he is 100% part of Vibeo team. -We have indeed 2 offices, one is the main office and one is the development office, we partnered with LimeChain in Sofia. Some people are working remotely but all from Bulgaria. We will have everybody in the same office after the ICO. -I haven't registered my domain on the website you've mentionned, we own different domain for vibeo including vibeo.net, vibeo.ca and vibeo.com (highly valuable domain) but only vibeo.io is active and linked to vibeo app project. -Rest assure that if you want to invest in vibeo you are investing in a good ico, we already have a minimal version of vibeo app available on AppStore and Google Play, we will soon announce our first partnership, our team is fantastic, so do your own due diligence Max but I ll ask you to stop spreading false information about my company otherwise I ll contact the moderator.  Eric-Sebastien

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Hi Annet,  I was not aware of this report. Thanks for sharing it! Actually they did a very good job, pretty much accurate, however on the weakness I'd like to clarify few points:  -There is no detailed financial plan: Well there is a summary on the whitepaper (page 17), it also depends on the money we will be able to raise. It won't be the same financial plan if we only reach softcap and if we go all the way to the hardcap. We will adjust the financial report after the ICO and make it public. -The project is not popular on social networks: This is true, we are working on it actually, we were too much focus on releasing our MVP before the ICO launch. -The project is not widely discussed on blockchain news resources: This is true, we are also working on it. -The project founders do not have experience implementing a successful business in the project field: Well I disagree, I have managed an incubator and helped many startups and young entrepreneurs, I have successfully released different SaaS platforms. We have some of the best tech in this industry in our team, Ben our iOS developer is one of the best chat/im expert. Blockchain is a new technology so nobody can claimed to be an expert, but we have certainly some of the best developers out there with LimeChain team as partners. We also have Kalin and Amarpreet Singh as Advisors, I would highly recommand to check Amar's LinkedIn profile for more information.  Overhaul a very nice report, lot of work and deep analysis has been done. Awesome job! thanks to DigRate!   Eric-Sebastien

Author: ivo.vibeo
Title: [ANN][ICO]Vibeo - New era of Instant Messaging/Social app powered by blockchain
Body: Hi,  The Vibeo protocol is designed to build the feeling of community among all users. The app incorporates a geo-localised map feature where you can discover a fully decentralised economy; each vibeo member will have its very own ERC-20 wallet; which will allow to find merchants and other Vibeo users in your locality and offer the possibility to engage with them.  This motivates users and merchants alike to exchange currency, exchange ideas and even render services within the platform thus helping the movement for decentralisation grow more.  The Vibeo API allows potential partners or merchants to easily get their services listed/added on the vibeo interactive map.  The protocol also incorporates key security features, not only within the app's technology, but also in its application, to ensure that users can be safe both within the app and in real life.  There are infinite possibilities in the use of the Vibeo app for both merchants, and users. In exploiting the unique features that the application offers, users can build a decentralised community with unlimited social and economic benefits.   I hope that answers your question.   Eric-Sebastien
